the maximum cardinalities of locally\ntwo-distance sets on a sphere for dimensions less than forty.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Jun 2009 02:44:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 10 Dec 2009 07:33:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-12-10"}
