ly, we compare our\nfindings to the predictions on the amplitude and running of non-Gaussianity of\nDBI inflation, showing how the constraints on a scale-dependent fNL(k)\ntranslate into constraints on the parameter space of the theory.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Jun 2009 08:16:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-01-06"}
